1. Install json server globally ( npm install -g json-server )
2. Create Http.service.ts in app folder for injecting the service to corresponding location( other components)
3. Create your json file ( mydetails.json ) in app folder
4. Go to run the command ( json-server --watch db.json --port 3030 ) in app folder to change the port and get it in service file
   // https://localhost:3030/mydetails
5. Go and refer my Angular2_HTTP_Service Repository  for Injecting the service to other components
6. Create View component and follw the http service to get all details from mydetails.json
7. Import correspong RouteModule, HttpModule to access the View Components
8. Create add component to push new deatails intom server
